00:00:47.120 --> 00:00:48.080
and remain by my side

00:00:48.240 --> 00:00:49.400
to share my burdens.

00:00:49.840 --> 00:00:51.872
I shall bear this in heart

00:00:51.872 --> 00:00:54.120
(Consort Jing)
and never disappoint your expectations.

00:00:54.280 --> 00:00:55.232
Rise.

00:00:55.400 --> 00:00:56.480
Please be seated.

00:01:05.520 --> 00:01:06.840
Your Majesty,

00:01:07.000 --> 00:01:08.080
for today's Spring Banquet,

00:01:08.080 --> 00:01:09.840
I personally oversaw preparations

00:01:10.040 --> 00:01:11.640
to share this

00:01:11.640 --> 00:01:14.240
glorious springtime with you

00:01:14.400 --> 00:01:17.560
and celebrate our flourishing realm
with other consorts.

00:01:17.600 --> 00:01:18.640
Thank you, my beloved.

00:01:18.800 --> 00:01:20.200
Thank you for your concern.

00:01:20.400 --> 00:01:21.800
My effort is worthwhile

00:01:21.880 --> 00:01:23.720
